-the-first-to-ever-gross-1billion-3556365">“Eras Tour”成为历史上首个收入超过 10 亿美元的巡演</a>，并且<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-to-become-the-most-lucrative-tour-in-history-3515012">有望成为有史以来最赚钱的巡演</a>。它<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-to-boost-uk-economy-by-1billion-3756392">极大地提振了英国、美国和全球其他国家的经济</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-concert-movie-3513715">2023 年的一部现场电影记录了这次大规模的长途跋涉</a>，该电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-the-eras-tour-biggest-ever-opening-weekend-concert-film-3515544">赢得了有史以来票房最高的音乐会电影首周末票房</a>。迪士尼+随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-concert-movie-lands-disney-release-date-3584268">在全球发布了该电影的“泰勒版”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-looks-ahead-to-final-eras-tour-shows-the-most-extraordinary-chapter-of-my-life-3816310">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 展望“Eras Tour”最后一场演出：“我生命中最非凡的一章”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
